title: Allen Carr - Easy Way To Stop Smoking - Unabbriged Audio Book -
description:
Written in 1985, this is the book that has started a revolution amongst smokers that want to stop. The book's author, Allen Carr, was a professional accountant that had been smoking 100 cigarettes a day when the stumbled upon the secret to stopping smoking, and ENJOYING THE PROCESS! Here it the unabridged Audio Book taken from the last revision of the book. Read by Mr Duncan Wells, and introduced by Allen Carr himself.

The entire 5 cd set is about 6 hours long. You've got to look at it this way, what could you POSSIBLY have to loose by listening to this?
